                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanonphat-supho" target="_blank">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024"><path fill="currentColor" d="M880 112H144c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32v736c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32h736c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32V144c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32zM349.3 793.7H230.6V411.9h118.7v381.8zm-59.3-434a68.8 68.8 0 1 1 68.8-68.8c-.1 38-30.9 68.8-68.8 68.8zm503.7 434H675.1V608c0-44.3-.8-101.2-61.7-101.2c-61.7 0-71.2 48.2-71.2 98v188.9H423.7V411.9h113.8v52.2h1.6c15.8-30 54.5-61.7 112.3-61.7c120.2 0 142.3 79.1 142.3 181.9v209.4z"/></svg>
